{"tid":1420161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉載自高登)目擊天安門事件老師懷疑士兵曾食藥：見人就打就開槍, 邊打邊狂笑","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T11:13:41.000Z","uid":201464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9644ce97bb36966295aeb629324eb41f484c928","tid":1420161,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"詳情：<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7095202/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7095202%2Fpage%2F1&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnAPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=63c6a5d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7095202/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n話說有消息指清場當晚進入天安門廣場既軍隊唔係之前o係北京見到o個批<br />\n之前o個批軍人曾經接觸過民運人士同市民<br />\n有人俾報紙佢地睇, 希望佢地咩發生咩事<br />\n有人甚至俾食物同水佢地, 動之以情<br />\n有部份關係尚算「良好」<br />\n亦傳出有部份軍人開始動搖<br />\n<br />\n而清場當晚既軍人係曾經被隔離一段時間<br />\n佢地完全冇接觸過外間任何資訊<br />\n佢地係唔知外面發生咩事<br />\n所以可以毫不猶豫地落手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTVB當時用電話訪問咗一位目擊事件既大學老師<br />\n老師形容o個班軍人塊臉同眼都通紅, 對眼好似發光咁<br />\n見人就打, 見人就開槍<br />\n仲要一路打, 一路狂笑<br />\n老師話佢地好似食咗藥咁<br />\n<br />\n而家諗番, 真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1dacc8114367db8c2618f1047c199a837ed9ab","tid":1420161,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205c7dde47fe86159bc51a238cd76fc91903e47e","tid":1420161,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0a42df9c572d66c0e2b14fe143aee5c84cb043","tid":1420161,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}